{"tid":2253641,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"「亞十被自殺案」黑警今次呢單野算唔算偽造證供？","createTime":"2020-10-22T09:48:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-22T15:11:05.000Z","uid":222970,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5119606d7a338ecac577369b07fe1cf44c10b827","tid":2253641,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T09:48:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20120602/QALF4IOIQ52K4KG7LE7QJYPF7U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20120602%2FQALF4IOIQ52K4KG7LE7QJYPF7U%2F&d=mhl3ai6H9Odyk596tiaOPWa%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=2bc42401\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20120602%2FQALF4IOIQ52K4KG7LE7QJYPF7U%2F&h=d43c700a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20120602/QALF4IOIQ52K4KG7LE7QJYPF7U/</a><br />\n<br />\n林國璋完成認屍程序後接受《蘋果》訪問，形容亞十容遺容平靜、沒有異樣，「好似瞓覺咁」。他又引述法醫指，亞十還柙期間曾出現反常行為，包括在10月6日以手「潑粥（潑開粥水），」並於2日後被發現以「長褲纏頸自殺」後送院，至9日早上證實不治，相信期間經過搶救。法醫又稱，亞十的死因是被長褲勒頸，而現場懲教人員在法醫詢問下，亦確認阿亞關押於高度防止自殺的房間，並無上吊自殺的可能性，又透露有閉路電視監視房間內的情況，每15分鐘也會有職員巡視；現場警員則確認亞十死因「冇可疑」。<br />\n<br />\n被問到警察要求帶返警署錄口供，林國璋表示今早到場後在櫃台進行手續時，突然有兩名重案員便衣警員向他問話，但形容他們整體上態度友善，相信是跟進案件的屯門警區重案組警員，希望向他們錄取口供；及後再有4名懲教人員到場，他們態度較凝重，但沒有作任何問話，僅在場視察。林又指，<span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"x-large\"><strong>期間警員曾提及要到警署錄口供</strong></span></span>，惟在認屍完畢後，又改口<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"gold\"><strong>表示已填寫好口供，並要求林簽名</strong></span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n林國璋指，在口供紙上發現警員擅自加上亞十「生活唔足夠」、「在小欖精神病治療中心自殘」等字句，他表示自己從及提及，亦不<span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"x-large\"><strong>同意亞十有自殘及自殺傾向，已即時要求警員刪除字句</strong></span></span>。他又形容，亞十為人雖然內向，但對人友善，以往有多次出入監獄經驗，「瞓街都瞓咗咁多年，冇咩對佢嚟講睇唔開，我哋所有識亞十嘅人，都唔相信佢會自殺」，重申亞十的死因要待死因庭裁決，屆時希望會在庭上播放事發時的閉路電視。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"gold\"><strong>雖然冇簽名，但牧師都未錄口供，係未經佢同意之F黑警已經幫佢做埋證供 算唔算犯法？</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"bd5b132d12bd0e393182696a4a91ee71277383dc","tid":2253641,"uid":259901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T09:50:35.000Z","msg":"算<br />\n不過律正屍唔會告<br />\n所以冇犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c6a00d84345038ac8210c01ec382ed4bf6ba83f","tid":2253641,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T09:53:24.000Z","msg":"你條LINK同內文唔同架喎CHING<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201019/NYXXFWHNFZDYLAHCWQXPCKYTEE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201019%2FNYXXFWHNFZDYLAHCWQXPCKYTEE%2F&d=mhl3ai6H9Odyk596tiaOPWa%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=ae8d4229\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201019%2FNYXXFWHNFZDYLAHCWQXPCKYTEE%2F&h=63dc9553\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201019/NYXXFWHNFZDYLAHCWQXPCKYTEE/</a>"},{"pid":"eaa2face0e6ffdee79666312074c370530168ab5","tid":2253641,"uid":72994,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T09:54:31.000Z","msg":"無人比人告就無人犯法<br />\n民事自己告就會比律政插手取消<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n亞十死不瞑目"},{"pid":"94e49d1dea468ef811aa7af0212617985cd15241","tid":2253641,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eaa2face0e6ffdee79666312074c370530168ab5","tid":2253641,"uid":72994,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T09:54:31.000Z","msg":"無人比人告就無人犯法<br />\n民事自己告就會比律政插手取消<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n亞十死不瞑目"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T09:55:46.000Z","msg":"Sor post錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74cc8f21d6d2dd02dd16bfb747f3a4a07337edcd","tid":2253641,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T15:10:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"731bcba7434189c9200927bb73c6b0f26364c140","tid":2253641,"uid":268591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T15:11:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"5c6a00d84345038ac8210c01ec382ed4bf6ba83f","tid":2253641,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T09:53:24.000Z","msg":"你條LINK同內文唔同架喎CHING<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201019/NYXXFWHNFZDYLAHCWQXPCKYTEE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201019%2FNYXXFWHNFZDYLAHCWQXPCKYTEE%2F&d=mhl3ai6H9Odyk596tiaOPWa%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=ae8d4229\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201019%2FNYXXFWHNFZDYLAHCWQXPCKYTEE%2F&h=63dc9553\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201019/NYXXFWHNFZDYLAHCWQXPCKYTEE/</a>"}}